          </p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5">
       <strong>The reaction:</strong> EU Foreign Affairs Chief Kaja Kallas expressed disappointment, emphasizing Slovakia's role in pressuring Moscow. Many EU lawmakers fear that Slovakia may <a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #06266D; color: black;" href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-17-jul-25-spotlight-h1-3-follow-hungary-s-example" target="_blank">follow Hungaryâ€™s example</a> in undermining EU decisions. However, they also noted that the governmentâ€™s approach was more constructive. 
